For sale is 1,000 CCI M34 7.62MM NATO-SPEC Large Rifle Primers.  Military-style semi-automatic rifles seldom have firing pin retraction springs.  If care is not used in assembling ammunition, a “slam-fire” may occur before the bolt locks.  The military arsenals mitigate this by using different techniques and components to include different primer sensitivity specifications from their commercial counterparts.  CCI makes rifle primers for commercial sale that matches sensitivity specs that reduces the chance of a slam-fire when other factors go out of control.
